data.description: Home Sweet Home! This spectacular POOL Home offers 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, 2 car garage and a fully screened Heated Salt Water in Ground Pool and Jacuzzi, surrounded by pavers. The front door opens to an open, bright kitchen that includes a dining room and sitting area with double paned sliders leading to the pool/lanai. As you proceed through you are welcomed into a large Family room with another set of double paned sliders that also lead to the pool/lanai area. The Master bedroom includes a TV, and Electric fireplace on the wall, as well as closet-built ins. This home features a 3 zone HVAC System with 1 thermostat in the Master bedroom, 1 thermostat in the Main area and 1 thermostat in the Family Room. The yard is fully fenced, includes a sprinkler system and a shed, The Roof is 1 year old, brand new Water heater, Driveway pavers and beautiful Porcelain Tile throughout the home! Close to all amenities including schools, shopping, restaurants, boating, fishing, airports, attractions, and Florida's beautiful beaches. Easy commute to Tampa and Orlando. Make this turn key home yours today!
